hopobject.body: Could I borrow your phone, please? generic soft viagra The choices are broader for healthy seniors and usually involve what's called a continuing care retirement community, or CCRC. These communities are not all alike and offer different levels of care and payment models. The most fully equipped CCRCs provide living units for healthy residents but also offer on-site facilities and health care staffing for those needing assisted living, full-time nursing care and even Alzheimer's facilities. Their strongest selling point is in reassuring residents and their families that a person can stay at the CCRC for the rest of his or her life and receive whatever care he or she may need.
